<h2 id="mte-noddi-disentangles-non-t2-weighted-signal-fractions-from-t2-relaxation">MTE-NODDI disentangles non-T2-weighted signal fractions from T2 relaxation.</h2>

<p>Robust intra-neurite T2 estimation in WM even with CSF contamination.</p>

<p>Non-T2-weighted fractions may improve the interpretability of neurodevelopmental studies.</p>
